features: ✅【3 Powerful Suction Modes】 HAIMEEC 6-in-1 cordless vacuum cleaner has 3 speed levels, allowing you to easily switch between the highest mode(24kPa), the medium mode(16kPa), the standard mode(8kPa). Meet your various cleaning needs of pet hair, fine dust, crumbs, large particles on hardwood floors, tile floors, marble floors and low pile carpets, etc. (Note: Not suitable for high pile rugs.)

✅【IQ LED Touch Display】 Get the information of cordless vacuum cleaner performance in real time, includes real-time readouts on runtime, floor brush operating status, power mode. And you can adjust the power mode of the vacuum cleaner by touch screen.

✅【Upgraded Battery Long Runtime】 HAIMEEC cordless Stick vacuum comes with removable rechargeable battery, delivers up to 15(Max mode)-50(Eco mode) minutes run time depending on your mode, Ideal for whole house work.

✅【Better Cleaning Results】 Configure the 5 -layer sealing filtering system, and the vacuum cleaner can capture 99.99 % of fine particles to 0.1um, and provide strong centrifugal force to effectively separate dirt, and finally output pure air and a faint fragrance. Note: Filters and sponges can be washed. Regularly clean the filter/sponge to prevent the vacuum cleaner from weakening and blocking.

✅【180° Rotatable Brush & LED Headlights】 This Cordless Vacuum Flexible Floor Brush makes it easy to clean under furniture and in dead spots.The LED headlight illuminates every corner of your home to ensure you don't miss any dirt and debris.

✅【6-in-1 Multi-Function & Storage Hook】The vacuum cleaner with Storage Hook can be assembled into 6 combinations for all your daily cleaning needs. Converts to a handheld vacuum with a crevice tool for stairs, corners, car seats and hard-to-reach spaces.
✳️【Purchase with Confidence】HAIMEEC offer 7*24hrs customer service and life-time 100% satisfactory after-sales service for the cordless stick vacuum cleaner.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Regarding cordless vacuum cleaner C1, is the suction power strong or weak? Compared with vacuum cleaners with the same specifications and power of about 150W on the market, the suction power of the haimeec cordless vacuum cleaner is above average. The suction power of this product can also meet daily needs. Is the battery life of the cordless vacuum cleaner long or short? The longest continuous battery life of C1 cordless vacuum cleaner is 45 minutes. How to clean cordless vacuum cleaner? You can directly clean the dust cup and filter, as shown in the picture，you can use the attached small brush to clean the floor brush. The floor brush can be removed separately, but it is not recommended to wash the floor brush directly with water. How to deal with product quality issues? When you are not satisfied in any way, you can send us an email. We will provide feedback as soon as possible.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worth Every Penny
reviews.reviewText: This lightweight cordless vacuum cleaner makes it incredibly easy to maneuver around my house without the hassle of plugging and unplugging. This has saved me a significant amount of time and effort, particularly when cleaning large rooms or moving between different areas of the house. The suction power of this vacuum cleaner is impressive, as it effectively picks up dust, dirt and pet hairs from both hard floors and carpets. The various attachments and accessories that come with the vacuum are quite useful. One of the major selling point for me was the battery life. The long-lasting battery allows me to clean multiple rooms in a single charge, which has been incredibly convenient. Additionally, the charging dock makes it simple to store and keep the vacuum ready for use at all times. Another plus point is easy of maintenance. The dust bin is simple to empty, and the filter is easy to remove and clean. In terms of noise level, i have been pleasantly surprised by how quiet this vacuum cleaner is during operation. It allows me to clean without disturbing others in the house. Overall, i have beed extremely satisfied with the performance and convenience of this cordless vacuum cleaner. I would highly recommend this product to anyone in the market for a reliable and efficient cordless vacuum cleaner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Battery lasts a while.
reviews.reviewText: I loved that it has a digital readout to tell you how much charge is in the battery. Was surprised at how much suction that it has. Super light weight. Hangs on the wall out of the way because of its compact size. Comes with a tool that hooks hair off of the removable brush head. Easy to clean out. Goes from carpet to hardwood to linoleum with no loss of suction. It is quiet. It slides easily under furniture. A breeze to use and I love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Effortless Cleaning, Powerful Performance
reviews.reviewText: The HAIMEEC 6-in-1 cordless vacuum is a game-changer for my cleaning routine. Its dual suction modes easily handle various floor types, and the IQ LED Touch Display keeps me informed on battery life and performance. The upgraded battery provides a solid 45 minutes in Eco mode, making it perfect for whole-house cleaning. The 5-layer filtering system ensures a thorough clean, and the 180° rotatable brush with LED headlights helps navigate tricky spots effortlessly. Its versatility, including a handheld mode and a storage hook, adds to its practicality. Compact yet powerful, this vacuum has become my go-to for quick and efficient cleaning.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent for the price
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I have laminate flooring throughout my home and this works perfect for that. I can vacuum the whole house only using about 30% of the battery on the regular setting. Cons: The suction is not the best on my rugs, unless used on the highest setting, but it does drain the battery quite quickly. The brush attachment needs improvement. (See video) I have to hold it in place to clean inside any kind of creases, and it does require the highest power setting. The storage holder only seems to work if the vacuum is locked and touching the floor. Pros: Cleaning the roller and filter is easy, it’s much quieter than I expected, decent price, battery life is good on hard surfaces, lightweight.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works like a magic
reviews.reviewText: I was very skeptical about buying this cordless vaccum since I didn’t have very good experience with my old one. But I was tired of cord plug-in vaccum getting tangled everywhere. One of my friends recommended me so just wanted to try out. Very impressed with how it cleans minutely. The battery lasted for a long time. Was easy to assemble and light enough to carry everywhere in the house.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Handy Vacuum
reviews.reviewText: Very nice vacuum, it is light and comes with different extension parts. Suction power is really good and it is controllable, you can increase it from the touch screen on the main unit. The screen on the unit is very handy and as mentioned it is touch, you can see the battery percentage and modify suction power. the carpet tool has a brush that rotates and speed up with vacuum power as well, it came with an extra HEPA filter. I really love it since I don't have to carry our big vacuum with me upstairs and it works as good as our big vacuum. It is perfect for pet hairs and cleaning the stairs. Strongly recommend it to a friend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I truly like this product it has all the proper equipments to be attached. It's great and sweeping vacuuming has a pretty good suction. The downside of it is when I first unpackaged the item of course I charge the battery like they said for 4 hours well I have it practically charged all night long and it only lasts on high speed maybe 30 minutes or 40 vacuuming so I'm really upset of the battery situation I feel like they should have another backup or customize their battery to last longer at least 2 hours if it's fully charged for all-nighter then it shouldn't be draining in 30 minutes or 40 on high speed!!! Unfortunately I had thrown away the the Box is not I would have just have returned it because again I'm very very upset you pay so much money and you would think that these charge battery would last for two to three hours. I think the Dollar Tree batteries will last longer than the actual charged one!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight but vacumms well!
reviews.reviewText: Purchased after using my sister's Dyson cordless that she loves. Bad thing about the Dyson, there is no hold on button and her hands get tired holding the trigger. The Haimeec at $500 less cleans well maybe not as good as Dyson but very close! It's easy to handle the display shows battery power on the display and so far haven't run until it kills battery. I found it to be a great vaccum for bath mats and door entrances where winter grass clippings seem to stick to everyone's shoes and deposit them on our hardwood floors. This Vac makes it a easy clean up and it's size allows it to go where our other vaccum won't. It very manuversble and the head makes 90 degree turns to help where others miss. We love it!Very easy to dump canister and can be easily cleaned with water. HEPA filter also can be rinsed with water.
